Group iron platebody is a platebody obtainable only by players who chose to be a standard group ironman in Group Ironman game mode. It is obtained by using the Armour right-click option on the Group Iron tutor. It has equivalent stats to an iron platebody, which is the best melee armour a starting player can use.

It is obtained by using the ''Armour'' right-click option on the [[Group Iron tutor]]. It has equivalent stats to an [[iron platebody]], which is the best melee armour a starting player can use.
